006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.qname.IEnhancedQName;
009
010import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
011
012/**
013 * This marker interface indicates that the instance has a flag, field, or
014 * assembly name associated with it which will be used in JSON/YAML or XML to
015 * identify the data.
016 *
017 */
018public interface INamedInstance extends INamedModelElement, IAttributable, IInstance {
019  /**
020   * Retrieve the definition of this instance.
021   *
022   * @return the corresponding definition
023   */
024  @NonNull
025  IDefinition getDefinition();
026
027  /**
028   * This represents the qualified name of a referenced definition.
029   *
030   * @return the qualified name
031   * @see IDefinition#getDefinitionQName()
032   */
033  @NonNull
034  IEnhancedQName getReferencedDefinitionQName();
035}
